  "policy": "warn",
  "description": "Canonical tag vocabulary per domain. validate.py emits a warning (not error) when an entry uses a tag not listed here. Helps AIs filter entries cleanly during the READ_PROTOCOL ranking step and avoids tag drift (e.g. n8n vs n8n-workflows vs n8n-platform). Add new tags here BEFORE using them in an entry.",
